# Tell, Don't Ask

Naming: [domain-model.mdc](domain-model.mdc). See [passport-law-of-demeter.mdc](passport-law-of-demeter.mdc).

Tell services/entities to **enable**, **disable**, **assign profiles** — do not scatter `setDisabled(true)` with duplicated guards in endpoints.

Apply on new/touched behavior; consolidate legacy ask-then-set when editing.
